freeglut: freeglut (Open Source OpenGL Utility Toolkit)
freeglut:
freeglut: freeglut is a completely OpenSourced alternative to the OpenGL Utility 
freeglut: Toolkit (GLUT) library. GLUT (and hence freeglut) allows the user to 
freeglut: create and manage windows containing OpenGL contexts on a wide range 
freeglut: of platforms and also read the mouse, keyboard and joystick functions. 
freeglut:
freeglut: freeglut is released under the X-Consortium license.
